rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">standard publicly availa=
ble encryption algorithms</a>?</p>
</div>
<div id=3D"footnote-6" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[6] The =E2=80=9CKeep it secret, keep it safe=
