<div id=3D"footnote-7" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[7] I am eliding the details of what it means =
for crypto to be =E2=80=9Ctotally mainstream.=E2=80=9D Maybe it means that =
all dollars are on the blockchain, banks issue stablecoins, the Fed issues =
central bank digital currencies, etc. The point here is that I think in any=
 variation of that world you=E2=80=99re not keeping your dollars at Circle =
or Tether earning 0%.</p>
