<div id=3D"footnote-8" class=3D"footnote-content" style=3D"font-style: ital=
ic;">
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[8] The other problem is that keeping the mone=
y in regulated US banks was not, this year, all *that* safe; some of Circle=
=E2=80=99s money was at Silicon Valley Bank when it collapsed. Tether avoid=
ed that problem by keeping its money in a mystery.</p>
